name: A.I. portrait of Pablo Picasso (#0)
description:
The result of sifting through hundreds of generated images spawned from VQGAN+CLIP, selecting the ones that (((felt))) like they were emanating the spirit of Picasso, then inviting these digital monstrosities into the temple of AI anthro-alchemy, where the real magick is underwent.

Text prompt: "Pablo Picasso in the style of Picasso"
